  "instructions": [
    "Cut stale bread into 1-inch cubes and set aside.",
    "Melt butter in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add cinnamon and ginger to the pan and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add bread cubes to the pan and cook for 5 minutes on each side, until crispy and golden brown.",
    "Add sugar to the pan and stir to combine.",
    "Cook for an additional 2 minutes, until the bread is caramelized.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy."
